Class CssSmartSpritesResourceReader

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
ResourceReader, StreamResourceReader, TextResourceReader
public class CssSmartSpritesResourceReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements TextResourceReader, StreamResourceReader

This class defines the resource reader for the resources generated by the smartsprites global preprocessor : the generated sprites and the modified CSS files.

Author:
